OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FThree police officers are being
OL,7,Finvestigated for potential misconduct
OL,8,Fafter a man was shot dead on Christmas
OL,9,FEve.
OL,11,FMarcus Meade was reportedly suffering
OL,12,Fa mental health episode when he was
OL,13,Fhit in the chest by a single bullet
OL,14,Ffired by a West Mercia Police firearms
OL,15,Fofficer hours after they had been
OL,16,Fcalled to a property in Redditch,
OL,17,FWorcestershire, to reports of concern
OL,18,Ffor his welfare on December 24, 2024.
OL,20,FMr Meade, who was a father-of-two from
OL,21,FBirmingham, died at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
