FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FOfficers attended Fownhope Close at
OL,7,Faround 2pm and attempted to negotiate
OL,8,Fwith Mr Meade, who was in possession
OL,9,Fof a knife for 'several hours'.
OL,11,FThey forced entry at around 7:40pm
OL,12,Fwhen they used flashbang distraction
OL,13,Fdevices and discharged tasers, the
OL,14,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,15,F(IOPC) said.
OL,17,FToday (Friday 27 March), the IOPC said
OL,18,Fthree officers who managed the
OL,19,Fstrategic and tactical planning of the
OL,20,Foperation have been identified for
OL,21,Fpotential misconduct.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FThe watchdog said all other armed
OL,7,Fofficers involved in the operation,
OL,8,Fincluding the officer who shot Mr
OL,9,FMeade, are being treated as witnesses
OL,10,Fand there is no current indication
OL,11,Ftheir behaviour warrants disciplinary
OL,12,For criminal proceedings.
OL,14,FMe Meade's parents, Anthony Meade and
OL,15,FDeborah Clarke, previously said they
OL,16,Fwant answers about what happened to
OL,17,Ftheir son, who was reportedly alone
OL,18,Finside the property suffering from a
OL,19,Fmental health episode.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FDeborah Clarke said: "I want to know
OL,7,Fwhat happened to my son, I want to
OL,8,Fknow why they thought it was OK to do
OL,9,Fwhat they did to my son. I want
OL,10,Fanswers and I want justice for my son."
OL,12,FAnthony Meade had said: "Christmas is
OL,13,Fmeant to be a time for loving, sharing
OL,14,Fand caring, and to hear of tactical
OL,15,Fexplosions, a Taser and a bullet being
OL,16,Fdelivered into my son's chest makes it
OL,17,Fdifficult for us as a family to
OL,18,Fcelebrate Christmas ever again."
OL,26,@tD@YOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
