OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,7,F"Our sympathies remain with the family
OL,8,Fand friends of Marcus Meade, who have
OL,9,Fsuffered a devastating loss.
OL,11,F"We know they want answers and we are
OL,12,Fcommitted to ensuring our
OL,13,Finvestigation is thorough and examines
OL,14,Fall the circumstances of this tragic
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,F"As well as investigating the planning
OL,7,Fand management of the operation, we
OL,8,Fwill also examine whether Mr Meade's
OL,9,Fmental health was appropriately
OL,10,Fconsidered, if Mr Meade's race may
OL,11,Fhave influenced police actions, and
OL,12,Fthe extent to which police resources
OL,13,Fmay have been a factor in decision
OL,14,Fmaking."
OL,16,FThe IOPC said the decision to
OL,17,Finvestigate the officers' conduct
OL,18,Fcomes after consultation with
OL,19,Fspecialist firearms experts from the
OL,20,FCollege of Policing and Avon and
OL,21,FSomerset Police.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774768381
OL,3,CPolice officers investigated for
OL,4,Cmisconduct after man shot dead
OL,6,FWest Mercia Police Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable Grant Wills said: "Our
OL,8,Fthoughts and condolences remain with
OL,9,Fthe family of Marcus Meade and all
OL,10,Fthose who have been affected by
OL,11,FMarcus' tragic death.
OL,13,F"We continue to cooperate fully with
OL,14,Fthe IOPC and their independent
OL,15,Finvestigation. It is vital that this
OL,16,Fprogresses without prejudice so it
OL,17,Fwould not be appropriate for us to
OL,18,Fcomment further at this time."
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOUzD@^O]
